{"tid":2082323,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"TLOU2 先唔講劇情, gameplay今集都極無誠意","createTime":"2020-06-28T03:12:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-28T06:13:28.000Z","uid":22839,"like":14,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3bd6f1f5b3ef339cf7e581d6bda7d6b8c967f847","tid":2082323,"uid":22839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T03:12:34.000Z","msg":"我唔能夠話係垃圾，因為同上集９５％似，只可以話無進步同無誠意。除咗部份流程個地圖係半開放式設計之外, 系統基本上同上集無分別.<br />\n<br />\n玩Ellie線, 頭兩個鐘, 同尾兩個鐘打法上有咩分別? 頭十五個鐘部份戰鬥係刺激少少之外, 基本上你求其玩一part都唔會覺得有前後o既分別, 完全感受唔到角色同玩法上既推進.<br />\n<br />\n轉撚咗用Abby之後仲撚嬲, 又係玩潛行, 打法一尻樣, 武器又要升撚過, 痴撚咗線呀. 見到佢同歐文個段回憶關卡真係嬲到癲撚咗, Ellie 同 Joel 玩咗回憶去睇動物園, 你自己隻Game走去抄尻自己一次, 然後用Abby走去睇水族館. 完全係fucking lazy writing。"},{"pid":"6ddfa84461816c42e58c8bf39a38bf314fd72d86","tid":2082323,"uid":49151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T03:15:31.000Z","msg":"呢幾年太多潛行game 厭都好正常"},{"pid":"4a5a737ba8ea5478319948596871baad50787dbc","tid":2082323,"uid":57,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T04:38:07.000Z","msg":"PS d 獨佔好多玩法都好類似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a245d83367d223fadf3338895b850299543d4dff","tid":2082323,"uid":39369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4a5a737ba8ea5478319948596871baad50787dbc","tid":2082323,"uid":57,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T04:38:07.000Z","msg":"PS d 獨佔好多玩法都好類似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T04:45:34.000Z","msg":"今集玩落有d unchart feel"},{"pid":"f3c9cc71be9e58029046f409914da61359ac9e0e","tid":2082323,"uid":57,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a245d83367d223fadf3338895b850299543d4dff","tid":2082323,"uid":39369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4a5a737ba8ea5478319948596871baad50787dbc","tid":2082323,"uid":57,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T04:38:07.000Z","msg":"PS d 獨佔好多玩法都好類似<img src=\"/a